---
title: Summer Salad with Farro, Peaches and White Wine Vinaigrette
description: Its peach season so we let them be the star in this salad. Baby arugula adds the perfect peppery kick to the sweet peaches. All of this gets topped off with the tangy, creamy, marinated goat cheese.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/summer-salad-d7c0cb16.jpg
